Entering the house, you will be welcomed by a spacious and luxurious foyer, with artistic curves and delicate decorative details. The living room is designed with large windows that bring in natural light and create a close connection to nature. Inside the living room, a white sofa with comfortable cushions and pillows creates a space for relaxing and unwinding. If you want to relax, you can walk down the natural wooden stairs and go outside to the garden. The natural landscape is decorated with vibrant flower gardens, colorful fish ponds, and large rocks. The fresh and peaceful atmosphere makes you feel like you are truly living in a beautiful scenery. Finally, when night falls, the yellow and LED lights sparkle on the trees and bushes, creating a romantic and relaxing space for you. It is a wonderful house, a place to enjoy life and find peace with nature.** - <@1076313084261564416> (fast)
